<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>L'Atelier des Récits</title>

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    background:#fafafa;
    color:#222;
}

header{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px 20px;
    background:white;
    border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;
}

h1{
    margin:0;
    font-size:42px;
    letter-spacing:1px;
}

.subtitle{
    margin-top:10px;
    color:#666;
}

main{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:40px 20px;
}

iframe{
    width:100%;
    height:700px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    color:#888;
    font-size:14px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>L'Atelier des Récits</h1>
<div class="subtitle">
Histoires, mondes imaginaires et explorations narratives
</div>
</header>

<main>

<iframe 
src="https://claude.site/public/artifacts/1dd05fd6-d9a0-419c-9038-24d4b42ca257/embed"
title="Claude Artifact"
width="100%"
height="600"
frameborder="0"
allow="clipboard-write"
allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

</main>

<footer>
© L'Atelier des Récits
</footer>

</body>
</html>